Card Simulator
by Alexander Wurts

An application that allows a user to play with cards on screen or play solitare.
Work in progress

Features to add:
-Timing for Solitare
-Scoring for Solitare
-Placement snapping
-automatic flipping
-automatic deck card handling
-Save state between app restarts
-when moving a pile take all cards below too
-possibly more game types
  -3 card draw
  -Possible use of edge screen on samsung devices for games where you shouldnt see other players cards
  
